          <physDesc>
            <p>Vellum, about 5 5/8 in. by 4 5/8, consisting of 99 leaves, some of which
                        are much stained and slightly torn, especially <locus>foll. 34</locus>, <locus>44</locus>, <locus>54</locus>, <locus>72</locus>, <locus>92—94</locus>,
                        and <locus>99</locus>. The quires, signed with letters, were originally 16 in number, but
                        several of them are now either wanting or very imperfect. Leaves are missing
                        at the beginning, as well as after <locus>foll. 1</locus>, <locus>2</locus>, <locus>14</locus>, <locus>32</locus>, <locus>33</locus>, <locus>34</locus>, <locus>41</locus>, <locus>42</locus>, <locus>65</locus>,
                        <locus>70</locus>, <locus>80</locus>, and <locus>97</locus>. There are from 12 to 16 lines in each page.</p>
            <objectDesc form="codex">
              <supportDesc material="perg">
                <extent>
                  <measure type="composition" unit="leaf" quantity="99">99 ff.</measure>
                </extent>
                <condition>
                  <list>
                    <item>
                      <p>Vellum, about 5 5/8 in. by 4 5/8, consisting of 99 leaves, some of which
                        are much stained and slightly torn, especially <locus>foll. 34</locus>, <locus>44</locus>, <locus>54</locus>, <locus>72</locus>, <locus>92—94</locus>,
                        and <locus>99</locus>. The quires, signed with letters, were originally 16 in number, but
                        several of them are now either wanting or very imperfect. Leaves are missing
                        at the beginning, as well as after <locus>foll. 1</locus>, <locus>2</locus>, <locus>14</locus>, <locus>32</locus>, <locus>33</locus>, <locus>34</locus>, <locus>41</locus>, <locus>42</locus>, <locus>65</locus>,
                        <locus>70</locus>, <locus>80</locus>, and <locus>97</locus>. There are from 12 to 16 lines in each page.</p>
                    </item>
                  </list>
                </condition>
              </supportDesc>
              </objectDesc>
